Table Configuration
Setting	Value
Table Name	TASKS
Partition Key	taskid (String)
Billing Mode	On-demand (Pay-per-request)
Encryption	Enabled (AWS managed keys)
Region	us-east-1



 Table Schema

Each item stored in the TASKS table has the following attributes:

Attribute	Type	Description
taskid	String	Unique task identifier (UUID)
title	String	Task title
status	String	Task state (created / updated)
createdAt	String	ISO timestamp of creation
